            <milestone n="1" unit="line"/>Theog[i]t[ô]n, Sohn des Theogitôn, grüßt Ptolemaios, Sohn des 
            <app><lem>Hêraklidês</lem><wit><bibl default="NO">Hêrakleidês</bibl></wit></app>. <milestone n="3" unit="line"/>Ich habe an Dich 
            verkauft den mir gehörenden, von Dir erworbenen Esel – weiß-mausgrau, ausgewachsen – 
            <milestone n="7" unit="line"/>und habe erhalten den Kaufpreis in Höhe von einhundertacht 
            <term target="touargurioudrachmai">Silberdrachmen</term>, das sind 108 
            Drachmen <gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/>. <milestone n="10" unit="line"/>Im zweiten Jahr des Imperator Caesar Nerva Traianus 
            Augustus, am [x.] Thôth.
        </p></div><div lang="en" n="tran.18510" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="translation"><p>
            <milestone n="1" unit="line"/>Theog[i]t[o]n, son of Theogiton to Ptolemaios, son of 
            <app><lem>Heraklides</lem><wit><bibl default="NO">Herakleides</bibl></wit></app>, greetings. 
            <milestone n="3" unit="line"/>I have sold to you the white-mouse coloured, fully grown donkey, belonging to 
            me and bought from you <milestone n="7" unit="line"/>and I have received the price of one hundred and eight 
            <term target="touargurioudrachmai">silver drachmas</term>, = 108 drachmas <gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/>. 
            <milestone n="10" unit="line"/>Year two of Imperator Caesar Nerva Traianus Augustus, Tho[th x].
        </p></div></body></text></TEI.2>